ygData.messageBody:
Update:

We have all the items needed for the quest in the following amounts:

4 fishes
2 tonics
5 nuts
1 honey comb.

BUT, they are all spread over the entire contident. Nuts are in EC with
Sabella, Fishes are in Qeynos(Bandare, my dummy SK created for this quest and
Rendi) and NK(Fesse) Tonics in NK and Ogguk(Fesse and Kellendil)

Will appreciate it if someone *looks at Ziltus* help by teleporting us around.
